<br>
I agree that Peffin is lame however, but because of the way you can manipulate the &quot;rooted&quot; giant's aggro such that they're a non-factor. You don't even need AE tash, just have someone off to the side chain casting snare on each giant.<br>
<br>
-k <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uziann.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ziann</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/29/01 4:41:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3330.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> peffin and other observations</span><hr size=1> peffins cake with 3 people.  just use a little aggro manipulation.  we had about 50 elites up around the fire from people doing her and its still cake.  id recommend a ranger, bard, or other class with dodge/parry disc as 1 group member.<br>
<br>
after you hand the note in have the bard/ranger hit their disc and run thru the mass of giants gaining aggro.  they then go to the back wall and sit down.  the other 2 people can then engage peffin without aggro from the giants.  kill her, loot, done.  just make sure the 3rd person doesnt stand up during this.<br>
<br>
yes this is kinda cheesy, but so are rooted elites that dont despawn.  fight swiss with cheddar.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
rodrick was a pain for me.  from my observation the Emisarry is on about a 2 hour respawn in normal conditions.  he spawns exactly in front of the CC exit tower.  this spawn gets very bugged after the server has been up for a while.  it could be theres a quota of rodricks, or just a bug in general...anyway at some point Emisarry stops spawning.  Last week I camped him for a long-arse time, like a bunch of hours each day.  I tried every rumored trigger.  Nodda.  This weeks patch... seen him 5 times in 2 days.  If you need Rodrick try to get there in the first few days of a server reset.<br>
<br>
The rest arent too bad, some can be done solo (boradain, rodrick), some take 2-3 people (peffin,murdrick), some need 1 group safer with more (dolgidun, juliah). <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uziann.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ziann</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0> at: 11/29/01 4:49:24 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
